metadata.name: APE QR #1
metadata.description: Simply scan the QR code associated to your favorite Bored Ape and you will be directed to the URL where the Bored Ape resides on Opensea. A collection of unique one of a kind QR codes numbered 1 through 10,000 that directly correlates to the same sequential Bored Ape. OG Ape owners will have a fun way to show off their Ape.
